  "description": "Functional ceramics for electronic applications: BaTiO₃ dielectrics for MLCC capacitors, MnZn/NiZn soft ferrites for inductors and EMI suppression, PZT piezoelectric ceramics for actuators and sensors, getter materials (Zr-V-Fe, Ba) for vacuum maintenance, and alumina substrates for IC packaging. These passive components are essential for every semiconductor device and electronic system.",
